{"tid":625353,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"聽講 aoa澯美 柏木由紀 松井珠理奈 班人去參加 produce 48 😯","createTime":"2018-04-11T11:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T11:09:38.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"49a6f3da6b3263851e34376f5e3503ad2d378af4","tid":625353,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Daf1mLcW4AEIq2t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDaf1mLcW4AEIq2t.jpg&h=dcd848e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個係咪澯美黎<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/065158_924e0e8e0725bc0876d3b3627943a4ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F065158_924e0e8e0725bc0876d3b3627943a4ca.png&h=11bd3f15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac899e7147bfba7fa143e92aaadccea3fb9162fd","tid":625353,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3216/d3216326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3216%2Fd3216326.jpg&h=a7b84c78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccb01aad68dc61aead390ad2bcc40eb4ed93dce7","tid":625353,"uid":12782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"白間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcca6c8d0fed27e123724e837f73226ce63975e","tid":625353,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"《Produce 48》日本名單出爐　驚見出道11年AKB48「ACE級成員」<br />\n<br />\n南韓大型選秀節目《Produce 101》最新一季，與日本AKB48推手秋元康合作，定名為《Produce 48》，將選出日韓各6位練習生組成跨國籍的12人女團。AKB48家族派出的練習生們，10日赴首爾正式開始錄影，然而當中竟見到多位「Center級」人物，包括柏木由紀，松井珠理奈和宮脇咲良的人氣成員，讓不少粉絲大感意外。"},{"pid":"032566a9736c447e95a937ecb6f8f29bfec3dcbf","tid":625353,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"先前網路上已流傳南韓部分參賽者，其中就包括T-ara、AOA、CLC、DIA等知名女團成員，引起許多討論。而隨著日本參賽者曝光，這些「Top等級」角色更是引起關注，其中出道11年的柏木由紀更是AKB48的看板成員，立刻讓節目關注度大增。由於各自都有相當強大的粉絲群，也讓節目還沒有開播，就已經聞到捉對廝殺的味道。"},{"pid":"8205dd2e875bd2f6084c26e53a3c6b563a66f510","tid":625353,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"《Produce 101》第三季名稱改為《Produce 48》將從參賽的日本48名、南韓48名女練習生中，最終選出12人。投票賽制更有新招，南韓觀眾只能投日本成員、日本觀眾只能投南韓，以求更多兩國之間的互動與參與度。不過本屆也將規則改為「可以同時兼任其他團體」，也確定將由在日韓都擁有高人氣的FTIsland主唱李洪基擔任「國民製作人代表」。"},{"pid":"ad56fe0a135dbc251e0274da158aba27f5d4db04","tid":625353,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/193807_4646aa1bc886985fd281bbf0bc2138eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F193807_4646aa1bc886985fd281bbf0bc2138eb.jpg&h=d525bfd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35ca3ce2f45ae683d3f64cf03262ee4852d84275","tid":625353,"uid":44044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad56fe0a135dbc251e0274da158aba27f5d4db04","tid":625353,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/193807_4646aa1bc886985fd281bbf0bc2138eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F193807_4646aa1bc886985fd281bbf0bc2138eb.jpg&h=d525bfd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:43:54.000Z","msg":"natty 橙 就黎參加出道節目多過somi<br />\n但係一次都唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ae0b9ff74670cf0f41670617497ed7d67d30b4","tid":625353,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"《Produce48》今日進行首次錄制，SM-JYP-YG三大社均不參加<br />\n<br />\n11日，據放送界相關者表示，《Produce48》於今日在首爾京畿道附近某拍攝現場進行了首次拍攝，李洪基 昭宥Cheetah 裴允貞 崔勇俊等導師齊出動。<br />\n<br />\n同時，在之前的《Produce101》第一季中取得第一名的 SOMI 所屬社JYP方面今年將不會有練習生參加《Produce48》，此前從未參加過前兩季節目的YG和SM方面今年也不會派出練習生出演該節目。該節目預計將於6月首播。"},{"pid":"d508b9a7d4ff7baf3c041392cffda48629d56a48","tid":625353,"uid":163101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"李海仁今次唔參加多次?"},{"pid":"73d756ca062389218cff13eff906cbf36fa71f05","tid":625353,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/193807_4646aa1bc886985fd281bbf0bc2138eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F193807_4646aa1bc886985fd281bbf0bc2138eb.jpg&h=d525bfd9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>natty 橙 就黎參加出道節目多過somi<br />\n但係一次都唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面個報導話 jyp sm yg 唔參加，咁可能冇佢😊"},{"pid":"ed129f628547b8d2cc279c4e71b9f4238efa8ef2","tid":625353,"uid":44044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73d756ca062389218cff13eff906cbf36fa71f05","tid":625353,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/193807_4646aa1bc886985fd281bbf0bc2138eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F193807_4646aa1bc886985fd281bbf0bc2138eb.jpg&h=d525bfd9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>natty 橙 就黎參加出道節目多過somi<br />\n但係一次都唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面個報導話 jyp sm yg 唔參加，咁可能冇佢😊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"佢又入翻jyp咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"8f350e2c8a7ec8365b1c5f3f527321b1bd08902f","tid":625353,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":1,